item.description:
What Is Shade Net ? Shade net is a knitted HDPE material used in different Applications but it is main application is in agriculture. It is used to Safeguard agricultural produce from Environmental adverse effects like intense sunlight, strong winds, heavy rain, etc. It helps to reduce wastage of crops and thus increase their productivity.
